==German==
===Etymology===
Old High German ''muozan'', originally *''muotan'', compare [[moeten]]
===Verb===
'''müssen''' (auxiliary verb in composite tenses: [[haben]])

# To [[have to]], [[must]]
#:''Wir '''müssen''' es machen''
#::''We must do it''
#:''Wir müssen es nicht machen''
#::''We do not need to do it''

